.</li><li><strong>One-to-Many Head</strong>: Generates traditional YOLO out=
puts requiring NMS post-processing, outputting <code data-wg-notranslate=3D=
"">(N, nc + 4, 8400)</code> where <code data-wg-notranslate=3D"">nc</code> =
is the number of classes. This head typically achieves slightly higher accu=
racy at the cost of additional processing.</li></ul><p>You can switch betwe=
